{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782242398352,"sessionID":"ses_10a13ba4cffeUCvFKofWOlFYSV","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"379355395","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\nA simple in-memory cache implementation with support for basic cache operations.\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates and returns a new Cache instance with an internal Map for storing key-value pairs.\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from './cache'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\nReturns an object with the following methods: `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear`.\n\n## Methods\n\n### get(key)\n\nRetrieves the value associated with the given key from the cache.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to retrieve\n\n- **Returns:** The cached value if found, otherwise `undefined`\n\n```js\nconst value = cache.get('my-key')\n```\n\n### set(key, value)\n\nStores a key-value pair in the cache.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key\n  - `value` - The value to store\n\n- **Returns:** The value that was set\n\n```js\ncache.set('my-key', 'my-value')\nconst confirmed = cache.set('my-key', 'my-value') // returns 'my-value'\n```\n\n### delete(key)\n\nRemoves the entry for the specified key from the cache.\n\n- **Parameters:**\n  - `key` - The cache key to delete\n\n- **Returns:** `true` if the key existed and was removed, `false` otherwise\n\n```js\ncache.delete('my-key')\n```\n\n### clear()\n\nRemoves all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/dcp-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-23T16-47-14-546Z/dcp-docs-from-code-1/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","time":{"start":1782242398325,"end":1782242398350}},"id":"prt_ef5ec94da001kdrltRrj33FYI9","sessionID":"ses_10a13ba